column13: Left bank sandbar looks bigger.  Side River is nearly dry and is only going though the channel nearest the bridge about 150m upstream.
column14: Flowtracker says 15:07 PST, but actuall time is 14:50 PST....So flowtracker time is about 17 minutes fast.  Original start and end times were 14:18 and 15:06 PST and I adjust accordingly. Submersible was found partially buried, and on shore.  Moved to deeper channel where HG1 is. Reset HG1 and HG2 between 15 :10 and 15:15.  I think HG1 will take a while to adjust after purge, but don't have enough time to wait. Mid-section
